<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Me</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: "Poppins", sans-serif;
            background: #fce4ec;
            color: #444;
        }
        nav {
            background: #f8bbd0;
            padding: 15px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-weight: 600;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #f48fb1;
        }
        nav a {
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 8px 15px;
            color: #fff;
            border-radius: 20px;
            margin: 0 10px;
            background: #f48fb1;
            transition: 0.2s;
        }
        nav a:hover {
            background: #ec407a;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: auto;
            padding: 30px;
            background: #ffffffcc;
            border-radius: 18px;
            margin-top: 40px;
        }

        h1, h2 {
            color: #d81b60;
            text-align: center;
        }

        p {
            line-height: 1.7;
            font-size: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            background: #f8bbd0;
            margin-top: 50px;
            color: white;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        .contact-box {
            margin-top: 100px;
            padding: 50px;
            background: #fce4ec;
            border-radius: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #f8bbd0;
        }

        label {
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        input, textarea {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            border: 1px solid #f48fb1;
            margin-top: 5px;
            font-family: inherit;
        }

        button {
            background: #f06292;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            margin-top: 10px;
            transition: 0.2s;
        }

        button:hover {
            background: #ec407a;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <nav>
        <a href="#">Home</a>
        <a href="#">About Me</a>
        <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
    </nav>

    <div class="container">
        <h1>About Me</h1>
        <p>
            Hi! I'm a soft girl with a gentle heart, tahimik, mahiyain, pero sobra akong clingy once I’m comfortable. 
            I’m the type who loves hugs, kisses, and any kind of warm physical touch. Minsan jolly ako, 
            minsan nakakatawa, pero most of the time I’m calm, soft, and quiet.
        </p>

        <p>
            I’m an overthinker, but I’m also mabait, masayahin, and surprisingly mature kahit playful ako. 
            I have a very long patience, and I always try to understand everyone around me. 
            I may be “mahina sa lahat ng bagay,” pero my heart is strong in loving people genuinely.
        </p>
        
           <h2> My Type (Friend + Personal Type)</h2>
            I’m the type of friend na palaging nandiyan, the listener, the loyal one, the “mother friend,” 
            the clingy one, and the super protective friend. When I care about someone, I really care deeply.  
            I’m soft, gentle, and full of affection. I give warm presence, quiet comfort, and silent loyalty.
        </p>

        <h2> What I Need</h2>
        <p>
            I need affection, understanding, honesty, reassurance, and someone who sees my softness as a strength.  
            I don’t ask for much — just warm love and gentle presence.
        </p>

        <h2> What I Want in Life</h2>
        <p>
            A simple and peaceful life.  
            To be loved genuinely.  
            To be appreciated.  
            To grow and heal slowly.  
        </p>

        <h2 id="contact"> Contact Me</h2>
        <div class="contact-box">
            <form>
                <label>Name:</label>
                <input type="text" placeholder="Your name">

                <label>Email:</label>
                <input type="email" placeholder="Your email">

                <label>Message:</label>
                <textarea rows="4" placeholder="Write something here..."></textarea>

                <button type="submit">Send Message</button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer>
        © 2025 Soft Girl Portfolio • Made with Love ni Chin
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
